me-1235424714/">据报道</a></ins><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://deadline.com/2023/06/roland-emmerich-unveils-space-nation-franchise-tv-series-game-1235424714/"><em>最后期限</em></a></ins><ins><a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://deadline.com/2023/06/roland-emmerich-unveils-space-nation-franchise-tv-series-game-1235424714/">。</a></ins>如果您想了解开发进展情况，甚至还可以观看视频。 </p><div id="44528a78952c4f5294a6e75c88e4b7b1"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fvu_sxa7RdU" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p> <em>《Space Nation Online》</em>将让玩家踏上“揭开 Telikos 星团之谜的史诗之旅”，将于今年夏天晚些时候发布 alpha 版本，计划于 2024 年全面发布。假设取得一定程度的成功，动画短片、电视节目和衍生游戏随后出现。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/film-director-roland-emmerich-is-creating-a-shared-universe-of-tv-gaming-and-web3-tomfoolery-180028686.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/film-director-roland-emmerich-is-creating-a-shared-universe-of-tv-gaming-and-web3-tomfoolery-180028686.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6dc66220-552f-4de1-84e0-dacc332364d2</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 18:00:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687972779</ingested><modified> 2023-06-28T17:19:43+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/199449b0-15d5-11ee-ad97-1ea2d7a59dc2" width="2002"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/199449b0-15d5-11ee-ad97-1ea2d7a59dc2" width="2002"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Space Nation]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A logo for 'Space Nation' complete with 50 characters standing around.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Space Nation]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[I consider myself a patient person, but 'The Password Game' might break me]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天是星期三，这意味着这是浪费几分钟时间尝试解决互联网最新困扰的最佳时机。如果您使用 Twitter，您可能已经注意到一些关于<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://neal.fun/password-game/"><em>密码游戏的</em></a>讨论，这是一种将测试您的创造力、耐心和理智的浏览器体验。 </p><div id="10d9ab739c8048fab7d1a3efb56e7972"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">密码游戏现已推出！祝你好运👹<br><br> >; <a href="https://t.co/kXhmbHqYTK">https://t.co/kXhmbHqYTK</a> <a href="https://t.co/d6lbnfHrbx">pic.twitter.com/d6lbnfHrbx</a></p> — 尼尔·阿加瓦尔 (@nealagarwal) <a href="https://twitter.com/nealagarwal/status/1673703594778927105?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 6 月 27 日</a></blockquote></div><p>表面上，游戏的目标是创建一个任何黑客都无法破解的密码，而且体验一开始就很简单。规则一规定“您的密码必须至少包含 5 个字符”，而规则四则要求密码中的所有数字加起来必须达到 25。然后，事情开始变得越来越混乱。规则 7 要求您包含一个罗马数字，只是规则 9 告诉您需要一些罗马数字相乘后等于 35。最终，您的密码还需要引用今天的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/wordle-party-game-board-game-hasbro-preorder-215501443.html">Wordle</a>和以表情符号形式编写的当前月相。哦，在某一时刻，游戏中添加了一个时钟，它是一条毛毛虫，你必须让它活下去。别问。有些要求是如此深奥，谷歌的自动完成功能已经开始适应它们。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> “这个游戏中有一些规则，确保我永远不会看到天国之门，”<em>密码游戏</em>的创造者 <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/nealagarwal/status/1673716068416716804?s=20">尼尔·阿加瓦尔写道</a>。阿加瓦尔的推特上满是人们咒骂他制造了如此不正当的挑战。然而，有些人已经成功走到了最后。 “我不敢相信人们真的能够打败密码游戏，”阿加瓦尔周三写道。 “人类的精神是强大的。”至于我，我正在删除第 15 条规则，试图避免做一些棘手的数学运算。但我向你保证，我会成功，即使它会杀死我或那条该死的毛毛虫。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/i-consider-myself-a-patent-person-but-the-password-game-might-break-me-174555782.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/i-consider-myself-a-patient-person-but-the-password-game-might-break-me-174555782.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 5ea86058-c9de-443d-8789-af761cae87fc</guid><dc:creator>伊戈尔·博尼法西奇</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 28 Jun 2023 17:45:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687972440</ingested><modified> 2023-06-28T17:14:03+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Igor Bonifacic]]></category><media:content height="746" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/02d026f0-15d4-11ee-b5e2-842f274ee1dc" width="1244"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="746" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/02d026f0-15d4-11ee-b5e2-842f274ee1dc" width="1244"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Screenshot by Igor Bonifacic / Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Password Game screenshot]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The Password Game]]></media:title></me